# Environment contract — see packages/geostat-kit/docs/ADOPTION-LINE.md
# Index: docs/CONFIG.md (in your repo after adoption)
#
# Naming: module ids in geostat.ops.json are logical (frontend, backend).
# Docker service/container names come only from secrets/deploy.env (COMPOSE_*) + compose-gen.

# --- deploy.env ---
# DEPLOY_SERVER=user@host
# DEPLOY_PROJECT=your-project-slug
# COMPOSE_API_SERVICE=your-app-api
# COMPOSE_APP_SERVICE=your-app-app

# --- frontend (.env.dev / .env.prod / .env.deploy) ---
# VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:8090

# --- backend (.env.dev / .env.prod) ---
# API_PORT=8090
